{"tid":1452461,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"入機場前順手做地方文宣","createTime":"2019-08-12T01:23:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T03:50:32.000Z","uid":303957,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7abb443dc35c71914ba5271d64e9ab1a680a74c0","tid":1452461,"uid":303957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:23:22.000Z","msg":"大家都好嬲<br />\n不如入機場前順手做最方便快捷嘅文宣<br />\n喺811啲事情冷卻之前<br />\n要畀更多街坊知道（有機會睇新聞）<br />\n手寫又好<br />\n公司/屋企print又好<br />\n寫毛筆大直幡都好<br />\n冒求18區周圍都有街坊知道咩事<br />\n寫張紙順手去機場路上貼時間成本唔高<br />\n但就係需要大家出手做！"},{"pid":"67c59fb8d7a9d572c479e248aa7e4dd87ed88e17","tid":1452461,"uid":287015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:35:31.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n推啊"},{"pid":"1b793e572e709399701236d4a4bbe987e5cc22e0","tid":1452461,"uid":167467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:52:49.000Z","msg":"【幫手推】<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請帶備更換衣物及梳洗用品入機場</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1451296\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1451296</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"25c236685710fd3b66d60aec3230a5b0dc6f0fdb","tid":1452461,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:50:32.000Z","msg":"大家可唔可以整多少少人神共憤嘅俾遊客<br />\n好多時佢地知 Hong Kong fight for freedom<br />\n但好多時吸睛嘅係<span style=\"color: red;\">殘忍同無恥嘅行為</span><br />\n同埋可以出<span style=\"color: red;\">數字</span><br />\n吸引左佢地再講其他野<br />\n要令佢地覺得我地起<span style=\"color: red;\">人道災難</span>入面<br />\n佢地係於心不忍 而唔係其他國家嘅野唔關佢地事<br />\n<br />\n文宣小妹有野想講<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1451498\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1451498</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">621元朗恐襲</span>"}]}